  "texts": [
    "For example, NPA [96] and LSTUR [97] incorporate attention mechanisms to determine the importance of words after CNN layers.",
    "NRMS [98] and CPRS [99] utilize multi-head self-attention networks to learn word representations.",
    "These models are effective in capturing long-context dependencies and understanding the semantic information in the text.",
    "In addition to text modeling, language models are also used as content interpreters to capture user interests based on their historical interactions.",
    "For instance, WE3CN [100] employs a 3D CNN to extract temporal features from the historical data."
  ],
